About $HINUBI

A nameless shinubi of the Hidden Treat Village — The underdog ninja $HINUBI

A kunai clenched between his drooling jaws and a sword within the grip of his paws.

He has trained his entire life for this very moment: unleashed upon the world to find all the hidden treatos, "Shinubi" would stop at nothing to become the Shibkage of the village.

And reach a $1 on solana while doing so.

Shinubi is a community-based meme token with the goal of restoring a sense of community and trust in crypto.

Our greatest asset is the people who believe in Shinubi’s mission, with the same level of commitment to a similar outcome.

The character of Shinubi represents those who have been overlooked — the underdog in this crypto space, those who have been scammed, rugged, etc. It also represents the small investors. Investors who alone are insignificant but together have the power to send any token to $1.

How to buy $HINUBI

Acquiring $HINUBI is simple: Buy on a centralized exchange such as Poloniex or go the decentralized route and download Phantom Wallet, buy SOL, send it to your Phantom address, and swap within Phantom or Jupiter.

Embrace the ease and efficiency of welcoming Chinu our Chow dog on the Solana Blockchain, to your crypto journey.
